name: ExtractoR
summary: The game consists of number of levels divided into several episodes, set in different environments. New environments are unlocked only after passing the previous ones. To pass a level, the player must collect a certain minimum amount of crystals in that level. The crystals collected during the game are loaded into the ship's hold, which increases its weight and therefore reduces its maneuverability.
